Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Moments to Central Station + Sydney CBD

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 1 Buckingham Street, Surry Hills to the market. This superb freehold office building is located metres from Central Station and is best positioned to take advantage of NSW’s infrastructure boom. The four level fully tenanted building features three-street frontages, basement parking, a rooftop terrace and large 1,696sqm* of NLA.

1 Buckingham Street benefits from the following key investment highlights:

•	Four storey freehold office building with a 1,696sqm* of NLA
•	Net income of $1,506,720 per annum* on a WALE of 4.53 Years by income
•	Brand new signed heads of agreement to RT Health and Aeona Pty Ltd on 4% fixed annual increases
•	Basement car parking for 12 secure spaces
•	Rooftop terrace overlooking Central Station and the Light Rail along Devonshire Street
•	Thriving City Fringe office market with record low vacancy and scarce supply
•	Prime location metres from Central Station and a wealth of amenity
•	Direct access to incoming Sydney Light Rail and Sydney Metro projects

1 Buckingham Street, Surry Hills will be sold by way of Expressions of Interest closing on Wednesday, 31 July 2019 at 4:00pm.

*Approximate

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Seven storey building with 18 car spaces

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present 111-117 Devonshire Street, Surry Hills to the market. This outstanding freehold building is situated just a moment’s walk from Central Station, hugging the boundary between Sydney CBD and the thriving Surry Hills. Capitalising on Sydney’s strong office market, the building is fully leased to seven whole floor tenants with mix use zoning and offers significant rental reversion and conversion opportunity. An exclusive opportunity within Sydney’s City Fringe, 111-117 Devonshire Street is one of the most premier office investments in the Sydney metropolitan market in recent times.

111-117 Devonshire Street benefits from the following key attributes: 

- Seven storey freehold office building with NLA of 2,085sqm*
- Basement car parking for 18 secure spaces
- WALE (income): 1.67 years*, WALE (area): 1.66 years* 
- Significant rental reversion opportunity 
- B4 Mixed Use Zoning lending itself to hotel or residential conversion
- Prime location between Surry Hills and Sydney CBD 
- 220m* to Central Station 
- Located on the doorstep of the Light Rail with the Surry Hills Light Rail Stop just 300m* away
- 4-star NABERS Energy rating

111-117 Devonshire Street, Surry Hills will be sold by way of public auction on Tuesday, 16 October 2018 at 10:30am at AuctionWORKS.

*Approximate

For more information, please contact the exclusive selling agents.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE, as the exclusive sales agent, is pleased to present Suite 506, 51-57 Holt Street, Surry Hills. This immaculately presented office suite is an outstanding investment that capitalises on the thriving Sydney CBD and City Fringe office market. Situated just metres from Central Station and the city, the property has unrivalled access to amenity and public transport. Additionally, the subject property is located on the doorstep of the new light rail network expected to open in late 2019, providing further transport options and capital growth in the future.

Suite 506, 51-57 Holt Street, Surry Hills benefits from the following key attributes:

- 56sqm* office suite with mezzanine and 9sqm* balcony
- Strong natural light and modern fit out
- Tenanted until April 2020 with a net passing income of $38,163 per annum*
- Metres from Central Station and Sydney CBD
- Adjacent to the future light rail network anticipated to open in late 2019
- Unrivalled access to shops, dining and public transport
- Thriving Sydney office market, with city fringe office vacancy rates at a historical low 2.8%*

Suite 506, 51-57 Holt Street, Surry Hills will be sold via public auction on Tuesday, 10 December 2019 at 10.30am at AuctionWORKS.

For further information, please contact the exclusive CBRE sales agents.
